CatDescriptText: View of a door with broken window and torn curtain in a residential hallway, looking out toward the street.  One can see flowered wallpaper and flowered carpeting on the floor.  The broken window looks out to the street where a 1947-1949 Cadillac Fleetwood four-door sedan is parked.  The photograph may have been taken to document an insurance claim.
TitMainTitle: Interior entryway of house with floral wallpaper and broken front door window, 6956 Upland Street, Homewood
